{"tid":799093,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇朋友睇過<<向達倫大冒險>>","createTime":"2018-08-29T19:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T03:34:26.000Z","uid":95571,"like":139,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"6088659b86dada248fd635dcc06452bb966b92b2","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"細個睇過 <br />\n勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfafe73c480ff456cc16bd055203e0539a5b795","tid":799093,"uid":139829,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:28:57.000Z","msg":"都唔知點解細個可以一次過睇咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過真係童年回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6bf7198bbad6f77b9497e27fde5242da5c6b6f","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:30:45.000Z","msg":"靈魂之湖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得個集好正"},{"pid":"c71b5bd2463f5ed0ba105848026951310929d9fc","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:33:41.000Z","msg":"呢套野真係好經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我睇過最好睇既奇幻小說"},{"pid":"dbecc752f177d180b5a5409ebe01ae7a27bbfabe","tid":799093,"uid":137743,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"好撚正，細個會專登係圖書館預約來睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係平時唔多鍾意睇小說既我唯一一套會睇既小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近重温番漫畫版都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得最正都係首尾呼應，一開頭個小矮人原來係主角<br />\n最唏噓係女主角黛比同男主角既一段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26e7b64ffeb88301ac7caccf95abb3a316ec965","tid":799093,"uid":203977,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個睇過 <br />\n勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭覺得鬼不理好恐怖，之後愈睇愈鍾意，最後佢死果下真係接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw最鍾意睇吸血鬼試煉果集，初初班吸血鬼吹到幫達倫特訓實冇死咁，完全冇諗過會咁九死一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93b8294321709441d06fea74ec1961d6735089f","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbecc752f177d180b5a5409ebe01ae7a27bbfabe","tid":799093,"uid":137743,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"好撚正，細個會專登係圖書館預約來睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係平時唔多鍾意睇小說既我唯一一套會睇既小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近重温番漫畫版都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得最正都係首尾呼應，一開頭個小矮人原來係主角<br />\n最唏噓係女主角黛比同男主角既一段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:38:47.000Z","msg":"你講起我先記得最尾主角比人溶左做小矮人<br />\n我依稀記得少少劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最深刻個預言好正<br />\n後尾先知原來果次個吸血鬼王子引吸血魔入黎已經係預言中既一次機會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d069d3191dec30513c22fdf41c783b49693c4d","tid":799093,"uid":20262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:40:32.000Z","msg":"劇情幾緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abb79a4b5be07010dd45bc69c1be44db23ecc4c","tid":799093,"uid":137743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a93b8294321709441d06fea74ec1961d6735089f","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dbecc752f177d180b5a5409ebe01ae7a27bbfabe","tid":799093,"uid":137743,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"好撚正，細個會專登係圖書館預約來睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係平時唔多鍾意睇小說既我唯一一套會睇既小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近重温番漫畫版都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得最正都係首尾呼應，一開頭個小矮人原來係主角<br />\n最唏噓係女主角黛比同男主角既一段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:38:47.000Z","msg":"你講起我先記得最尾主角比人溶左做小矮人<br />\n我依稀記得少少劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最深刻個預言好正<br />\n後尾先知原來果次個吸血鬼王子引吸血魔入黎已經係預言中既一次機會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:40:46.000Z","msg":"值得重温呀巴打"},{"pid":"2fc3bed7e6f60152c7656836895f85789a3ae13e","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:43:19.000Z","msg":"害不了你。大高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9859ebf485e68dd4948565b02e23e5b3cf0ede64","tid":799093,"uid":181221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:46:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cafd1dceaf99319c88c478d8e7354bd772351ccd","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:47:07.000Z","msg":"莫哈凱＝柯達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4f4121327d8ac88d1a453fd3ffa02ad81b8dd5","tid":799093,"uid":95571,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"唔明點解呢套小說紅唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似同哈利波特差唔多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個作者之後套&lt;&lt;魔域大冒險&gt;&gt;又係幾好睇 但劇情好似冇&lt;&lt;向達倫大冒險&gt;&gt;咁多伏筆 好似係打架+血腥為主"},{"pid":"61efab3fcede8da84342b1decf5b6e9cb67b071c","tid":799093,"uid":171805,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T22:15:26.000Z","msg":"套小說當年好hit㗎,每次去親圖書館book書都要等好耐。我記得個作者仲嚟過香港書展搞簽名會,都有幾多人排隊下。不過套書冇哈利仔咁出名都正常嘅,始終哈利仔01年就拍咗電影,向達倫要到09年先有電影出,而且仲要拍得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我記得向達倫之後嘅《魔域大冒險》都好好睇,不過係多主角模式,所以睇起嚟會有啲亂,我依家淨係記得有個識砌窗嘅男仔嗰個故仔勁好睇。但係完咗魔域大冒險之後,就冇咩點聽過個作者了,我連佢翻兜寫《鬼不理大冒險》都係幾年前行過page one見到先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c946746d496b079d5f09aa128023c71cc4b3fb","tid":799093,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:02:21.000Z","msg":"小說漫畫都有睇過 幾正<br />\n漫畫入面既向達倫好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0087c34e7bab5e483d4e89cc2f4c3de599b0060","tid":799093,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:30:09.000Z","msg":"正到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最衰同期比哈利波特蓋過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d15474ccd2b8a5991ba1632089b4a735c2f7749","tid":799093,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"細細個上堂偷偷地睇 <br />\n鬼不理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1654602649aa0c7746bde2c1c1c70014c38b5b3d","tid":799093,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"係幾好睇，但我覺得可以寫得長啲<br />\n吸血鬼有幾百年命，但故事由主角細個講到大人就完，有啲晒"},{"pid":"cde308ba8949b22b5e39d0924e65f0bcd5d8f8cd","tid":799093,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"細過都每集出新都有買，最估唔到佢best friend 變左魔王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  套書屋企仲係到好似"},{"pid":"efe19b08673d2c8234db35524eb4b54cd20d2af1","tid":799093,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"真係好正"},{"pid":"11e0a1b95ccf4f59022ceb3c8c0d96411ddd779c","tid":799093,"uid":72696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"整個系列無限翻睇，細個真係睇到驚心動魄"},{"pid":"7ff122c63535e372f11a86c60ae39afd49cbfa0e","tid":799093,"uid":17718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"有成套書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62525c9f4dcaa27c97bbd58b4d3a472432229c2","tid":799093,"uid":28223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"呢套係好正 佢每個階段都好刺激好緊張 記得佢個好朋友變左做吸血魔重係度扮獵人埋主角身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3150e5751bf17c1aed9ce93b8d72c18aefd63b","tid":799093,"uid":4158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:52:49.000Z","msg":"召喚向達倫既fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34bb30ccc3a794309520cfe5bfa67ad48f53692","tid":799093,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"個主角有冇同debbie扑過野"},{"pid":"44341860f7acc90b35b41e7bf22a7ebfa246c278","tid":799093,"uid":46674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"有睇埋鬼不王大冒險同魔域大冒險<br />\n但最新果套zombie係咪無中文？"},{"pid":"ec6726610fec56de80b2657f7a30a9eebc723296","tid":799093,"uid":85776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔記得我有冇一套書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b53541f3db7d5c06d7c45b7e1ca129aa2e67fb1","tid":799093,"uid":164090,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"好好睇，個結局完全估佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇睇魔域大冒險，一開始用三個唔同既人做主角，跟手再結集一齊救世界，成套Avenger咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我到依家都唔明點解依啲打到肚破血流既書會歸類為兒童讀物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d520ef6dc9c65818c946c8122502f01a168fce7","tid":799093,"uid":73910,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"成個初中都係睇住向達倫長大，<br />\n到佢出魔域大冒險時，每集都買黎支持，去到後期仲apply埋做皇冠出版社既書評，可以係出版前優先睇到試閱本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/130332_1a468b67971628d1319fded49804abb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F130332_1a468b67971628d1319fded49804abb5.png&h=ece81acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者親筆簽名都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/30/130412_d91252a249e823eb5e900d3a481b046b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F30%2F130412_d91252a249e823eb5e900d3a481b046b.png&h=a327fd6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ac31bd22d85294753fae6cf19614104f0617a84","tid":799093,"uid":2435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b53541f3db7d5c06d7c45b7e1ca129aa2e67fb1","tid":799093,"uid":164090,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"好好睇，個結局完全估佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇睇魔域大冒險，一開始用三個唔同既人做主角，跟手再結集一齊救世界，成套Avenger咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我到依家都唔明點解依啲打到肚破血流既書會歸類為兒童讀物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"係咪有個可以用手砌碎片開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma